    <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, and other details you provide when contacting us or subscribing to our newsletter.</li>
      <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information about how you interact with our website, such as IP address, browser type, pages visited, and time spent.</li>
      <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> Small data files stored on your device to enhance user experience and analyze website performance.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use the collected data for the following purposes:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Provide and improve our AI services, including responding to inquiries and delivering personalized content.</li>
